entries.abort: Why have you aborted the recovery operation? That shuttle is now lost to the rebels.
entries.arrival_phase_1: The rebels have taken the Lamdba shuttle. Wait until it comes into range.
entries.arrival_phase_2: The shuttle is in range. Disable it and recapture it from the rebellion.
entries.capture_complete: Lambda shuttle back in imperial hands. Lets get it out of here.
entries.capture_phase_1: Boarding party reporting in. We are facing resistance, hold any other fighters off until we have successfully retaken the ship.
entries.capture_phase_2: Rebels have been elimated. Initilizing shuttle restart squence now.
entries.capture_started: Boarding party reporting in. Beginning assault on shuttle.
entries.complete: Good work pilot. We are jumping out of the sector...now.
entries.escort_remaining: Tactical Computer: %DI ships remaining in the shuttles escort.
entries.escort_wiped_out: Tactical Computer: The shuttles escort has been eliminated.
entries.failed_destroy: Your orders were to retake the shuttle not destroy it. Return to your superior immediately for debriefing.
entries.failed_escape: You have failed to recapture the shuttle from rebel hands. Return to your superior immediately for debriefing.
entries.recovery_success: The Lambda shuttle and engineers onboard have been safely recovered. Good work, pilot.
entries.split_quest_alert: During your assault on the shuttle a rebel scout was detected nearby. You are to capture that scout's computers and retrieve any information it might have.
entries.target_disabled: Lambda shuttle has been disabled. Boarding operation will begin shortly.
entries.title: Daring Rescue
